{"about_the_game":"Winter's Trumpet is a short Urban Fantasy point'n'click interactive love story set against the backdrop of an epidemic.<br><br>It was winter when the flu from Tarsia swept across Aeser... now you are quarantined with your roommate, Rosemary, who is bored out of her mind\u2014and is more than a little suspicious of your mysterious suitor, Marcus. After all, the man clearly has secrets.<br><br>The Urban part of our Urban Fantasy game is a unique 1920s style fantasy world.<br><br>You will see the story through three sets of eyes: you play as Tetrine Reish, a mortal 'scrivener', or seer, able to see magic others can't, Kalevel Venhera, a vengeful demoness, and Markaius, an ancient and elusive demon.<br><br>Discover more of the World of Aeser, as seen in our previous game, <i>Tell a Demon</i> (also on Steam) and <i>Asher</i> (available for free on our website). This story chronologically takes place before the events of both <i>Asher</i> and <i>Tell a Demon</i>.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Moping","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1342910/d34c7de0429057ba6bdc72acec64e3296d796e5f.jpg"},{"name":"Diversion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1342910/6518391094dc37eea48b02344daaf629534d6d37.jpg"},{"name":"Taciturn","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1342910/3f14395fa4d75a47947961921caded61c9019a90.jpg"},{"name":"Destroy the Evidence","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1342910/0f78a997e9e7be359d5fef215e91e9ac13a67683.jpg"},{"name":"Named","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1342910/8b2a39fbb875065f7ec880273c18fae4f10653f5.jpg"},{"name":"Immortality","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1342910/1fb07bea403f6d87443c6af026b8acc792b71396.jpg"},{"name":"Nature's Course","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamst